OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showers across northern
OL,6,Fand eastern areas will fade, leaving
OL,7,Fmost places dry with prolonged
OL,8,Fsunshine. Cloud will increase over
OL,9,Fparts of England and Wales, bringing a
OL,10,Ffew showers later, possibly thundery.
OL,11,FWidely very warm, feeling hot in the
OL,12,Fsoutheast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FEvening showers slowly
OL,15,Fclearing eastwards. Cloudy with
OL,16,Foutbreaks of rain affecting parts of
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland,
OL,18,Fotherwise dry with clear spells.
OL,19,FAnother warm night, especially in the
OL,20,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
