OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FDry with sunny spells for
OL,6,Fmost, however outbreaks of rain will
OL,7,Faffect the far north, with showers
OL,8,Facross the southeast, where it will be
OL,9,Fanother very warm day. Cooler
OL,10,Felsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
